    "author_association": "MEMBER",
    "body": "Agree with cutting the committee size!\r\n\r\nIt's worth noting that cutting the committee size has another important benefit. If on average a committee has size n, then a validator with > 1/n of the stake will need to process almost the entire chain. Pushing n down reduces the number of validators who will need to do that.",
